<td colspan="2" style="padding-left: 0.5em;"><a href="/wiki/Northern_Isles" title="Northern Isles">Northern Isles</a>, <a href="/wiki/Caithness" title="Caithness">Caithness</a>, <a href="/wiki/Scottish_Lowlands" title="Scottish Lowlands">Scottish Lowlands</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ulster" title="Ulster">Ulster</a>, <a href="/wiki/England" title="England">England</a> adjacent to the border with Scotland.</td>
