<td colspan="2" style="padding-left: 0.5em;">est. 200,000 <small>(<a href="http://www.ethnologue.com/show_country.asp?name=GB" class="external text" title="http://www.ethnologue.com/show_country.asp?name=GB" rel="nofollow">ethnologue</a>)</small> to over 1.5 million <small>(<a href="/wiki/General_Register_Office_for_Scotland" title="General Register Office for Scotland">General Register Office for Scotland</a>, 1996)</small></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 0.5em;"><a href="/wiki/Language_family" title="Language family">Language family</a>:</td>
<td colspan="2" style="padding-left: 0.5em; text-align: left;"><a href="/wiki/Indo-European_languages" title="Indo-European languages">Indo-European</a><br />
